This is the third incarnation of a blog that dabbles into all things uncanny. Reviews of music albums, books, movies and video games; musings on folklore, mythology and the occult; as well as short stories.<br />
Most of the more recent material is in English, while most of the older (as well as most short stories) are in Greek. The blog does not actively accept comissions about reviews.</p>
